T02TD1614E:138a-0: @138a * // dpal gdan bzhi pa'i za ba don sngon pa shing gcig gi dka' 'grel bzhugs /
T02TD1614E:138a-2: # // dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1614E:138a-3: gtso mo lha mo thams cad bde //
T02TD1614E:138a-4: de nyid thams cad rab brtson mdzad //
T02TD1614E:138a-5: gru gsum padma'i dbus gnas pa'i //
T02TD1614E:138a-6: zla ba nyi ma me yis brgyan //
T02TD1614E:138a-7: padma chen po nyer gnas te //
T02TD1614E:138a-8: yi dags chen pos gdan byas par //
T02TD1614E:138a-9: gdan skyes rnal 'byor ma bsgoms na //
T02TD1614E:138a-10: myur du dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1614E:138a-11: gdan bzhi pa yi rgyud kyi ni //
T02TD1614E:138a-12: lung gi don gyi rjes 'brangs te //
T02TD1614E:138a-13: shing gcig la sogs dka' 'grel ni //
T02TD1614E:138a-14: rnal 'byor grub phyir bshad par bya //
T02TD1614E:138a-15: dam tshig ma dang sgrub pa pos //
T02TD1614E:138a-17: gtor ma'i las ni khyad par du //
T02TD1614E:138a-18: nges pa nyid ni sbyar bar bya //
T02TD1614E:138a-19: zla ba yang ngo'i tshes brgyad dang //
T02TD1614E:138a-20: bco lnga dang ni bcu bzhi la //
T02TD1614E:138a-21: rang khyim rnal 'byor ma mchod nas //
T02TD1614E:138a-22: phyi nas gtor ma brtsam par bya //
T02TD1614E:138a-23: rang gzhan de bzhin phyi rol dang //
T02TD1614E:138a-24: lus la gnas pa'i lha rnams mchod //
T02TD1614E:138a-25: shing gcig la sogs gnas rnams su //
T02TD1614E:138a-26: gtor dang btung bas yongs su mchod //
T02TD1614E:138a-27: de ltar gyur pa'i sngags kyis ni //
T02TD1614E:138a-28: rnal 'byor ma kun mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:138a-29: de ltar sngags kun ma shes par //
T02TD1614E:138a-30: sngags pas phyi rol spyod byed na //
T02TD1614E:138a-31: bskal pa bye ba brgya bsgrubs kyang //
T02TD1614E:138a-32: lha rnams mnyes par mi 'gyur ro //
T02TD1614E:138a-33: de phyir rgyud rnams thams cad du //
T02TD1614E:138a-34: bcom ldan 'das kyis rtag sbas pa //
T02TD1614E:138a-36: dngos grub thob pa'i rgyu ru ni //
T02TD1614E:138a-37: 'di ni rgyas par byas pa la //
T02TD1614E:138a-38: nyon cig bzang po bdag gis bshad //
T02TD1614E:138a-39: aom zhes pa ni mchod pa'i dag / shing gcig la sogs bdun du ni //
T02TD1614E:138a-40: rgyang grags gcig gi nang rol nas //
T02TD1614E:138a-41: shing gzhan dag ni rnam spangs pa //
T02TD1614E:138a-42: shing gcig pa ni thams cad kyis //
T02TD1614E:138a-43: bshad pas shes par mi 'gyur phyir //
T02TD1614E:138a-44: lus ni shing zhes bya bar bshad //
T02TD1614E:138a-45: lag pa yal ga la sogs bya //
T02TD1614E:138a-46: rig byed mtha' yas gsungs pa dang //
T02TD1614E:138a-47: rgyud gzhan dag la de skad gsungs //
T02TD1614E:138b-0: steng gi rtsa ba yal ga 'og / aa shvad zhes @138b gsungs mi zad pa //
T02TD1614E:138b-1: me tog 'bras bus yongs su brgyan //
T02TD1614E:138b-2: shing zhes bya bar bshad pa yin //
T02TD1614E:138b-3: lus kyi dbus na aa gnas pa'i //
T02TD1614E:138b-4: gsang ba'i shing ni mi shes phyir //
T02TD1614E:138b-5: lte ba nas ni sor bzhin //
T02TD1614E:138b-6: de las lus rten rab tu gnas //
T02TD1614E:138b-7: de las steng 'byung yal ga gsum //
T02TD1614E:138b-8: shing gi bu gur yongs su ldan //
T02TD1614E:138b-9: lte snying smin ma'i dbus gnas par //
T02TD1614E:138b-10: thig le gsum ni gsungs pa dag / steng du 'og tu 'gro ba las //
T02TD1614E:138b-11: yal ga bcu zhes bya bar bshad //
T02TD1614E:138b-12: me tog 'bras bu rtag tu ldan //
T02TD1614E:138b-13: 'dab ma brgyad pa shin tu mdzes //
T02TD1614E:138b-14: gang tshe sna las phyir byung srog / shing gcig pa zhes bya bar bshad //
T02TD1614E:138b-15: gsang ba'i shing gi shing chen po //
T02TD1614E:138b-16: gsang ba yi ni gnas na gnas //
T02TD1614E:138b-17: mu stegs nyan sogs thams cad kyis //
T02TD1614E:138b-18: shing de rnam par shes mi 'gyur //
T02TD1614E:138b-19: chos 'byung ba yi tshal chen por //
T02TD1614E:138b-20: de yi dbus su yongs gnas par //
T02TD1614E:138b-22: me tog 'bras bus yongs su brgyan //
T02TD1614E:138b-23: de la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1614E:138b-24: thar pa'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
T02TD1614E:138b-25: bla ma'i zhal snga'i bka' drin gyis //
T02TD1614E:138b-26: mngon sum nyid du bdag gis bshad //
T02TD1614E:138b-27: pha zhes bya ba su krar brjod //
T02TD1614E:138b-28: ma ni raktar yongs su shes //
T02TD1614E:138b-29: yi ge gnyis ni kun sbyong ba //
T02TD1614E:138b-30: dur khrod du ni rnam par grags //
T02TD1614E:138b-31: dur khrod shi ba'i tshul du shes //
T02TD1614E:138b-32: yi dags kyi ni gnas su bshad //
T02TD1614E:138b-33: gang yang pha yis bsdus pa yi //
T02TD1614E:138b-34: gzugs dang kha dog mdzes pa'o //
T02TD1614E:138b-35: ma las byung ba'i gsum gyi dngos //
T02TD1614E:138b-36: de bzhin pha las byung ba'ang gsum //
T02TD1614E:138b-37: 'gyur ba drug po bsdus pa ni //
T02TD1614E:138b-38: dur khrod du ni rnam par grags //
T02TD1614E:138b-39: de phyir shi ba'i tshal du bshad //
T02TD1614E:138b-40: lus po yis ni brten byas pa //
T02TD1614E:138b-41: dbang po bcu po la sogs kun //
T02TD1614E:138b-43: srog ni dur khrod zhes byar brjod //
T02TD1614E:138b-44: rim gyis 'byung sogs ngo bo ni //
T02TD1614E:138b-45: tshigs bcad dang por gang gsungs pa //
T02TD1614E:138b-46: de lta bar ni gsang ba'i gzugs //
T02TD1614E:138b-47: shes rab padma'i mkha' khams su //
T02TD1614E:138b-48: ri dags 'dzin pa'i tshul gyis su //
T02TD1614E:138b-49: 'byung po thams cad ltung ba'i gnas //
T02TD1614E:138b-50: dur khrod du ni yongs su brtag / ri zhes bya ba'i ri bor bshad //
T02TD1614E:138b-51: lha rnams gnas su sa 'dzin te //
T02TD1614E:139a-2: gsum 'dus pa ni yang dag ldan //
T02TD1614E:139a-3: dbang po bya yis yongs su gang //
T02TD1614E:139a-4: ri dags la sogs sna tshogs ldan //
T02TD1614E:139a-5: lus rir gnas pa'i lha rnams ni //
T02TD1614E:139a-6: gtor dang btung bas mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:139a-7: srog kyang ri zhes bya bar bshad /
T02TD1614E:139a-8: rgyu dang mi rgyur bcas pa 'dzin //
T02TD1614E:139a-9: 'bras bu shing gis kun tu gang //
T02TD1614E:139a-10: ba spu rtsa yi phreng bas gang //
T02TD1614E:139a-11: chu ni yongs su 'bab par ldan //
T02TD1614E:139a-12: grub pa'i rnal 'byor ma bsnyen pa //
T02TD1614E:139a-13: pa zhes pa ni padmar bshad //
T02TD1614E:139a-14: rba zhes bya ba rdo rjer shes //
T02TD1614E:139a-15: ta zhes pa ni bde ba che //
T02TD1614E:139a-16: de phyir ri la ri zhes brjod //
T02TD1614E:139a-17: gang yang ri yi phyogs gcig gnas //
T02TD1614E:139a-18: de la gnas pa'i lha rnams ni //
T02TD1614E:139a-19: mkhas pa yis ni mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:139a-20: dbang po sgo dgu'i gnas rnams ni //
T02TD1614E:139a-21: sna tshogs cho ga yi ni gnas //
T02TD1614E:139a-22: de phyir gcong rong zhes su bshad //
T02TD1614E:139a-23: srog gi gcong rong gcong rong ni //
T02TD1614E:139a-24: ka zhes pa ni lus kyi dngos //
T02TD1614E:139a-25: de ni srog gi rlung gis bzung //
T02TD1614E:139a-26: de phyir gcong rong zhes su btags //
T02TD1614E:139a-27: ye shes bdud rtsi'i chu 'bab pas //
T02TD1614E:139a-28: bha ga gcong rong zhes su gsungs //
T02TD1614E:139a-29: gang yang 'dod chags zhu ba yis //
T02TD1614E:139a-30: khu ba yi ni gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:139a-31: ka zhes pa ni myos pa'i mdog / da zhes pa ni zhu ba'i bdag / ri zhes pa ni dga' ba'i bdag / gcong rong de ni de ltar bshad //
T02TD1614E:139a-32: phug ni phyi nas bshad tshul gyis //
T02TD1614E:139a-33: sgrub pa po yi gnas su gsungs //
T02TD1614E:139a-34: bye ba brgyad cu'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1614E:139a-35: gang du gnas ni rab brtags pa //
T02TD1614E:139a-36: de ni phug ces bya ba'i ming //
T02TD1614E:139a-37: lus kun de dang 'dra bar gsungs //
T02TD1614E:139a-38: rkang pa'i mthil nas spyi bo'i bar //
T02TD1614E:139a-39: gsang char khyab pa rlung gi gzugs //
T02TD1614E:139a-40: rtag tu rlung gi gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:139a-41: phug ces bya bar bshad pa yin //
T02TD1614E:139a-42: gsang ba'i gsang bar gnas pa'i lha //
T02TD1614E:139a-43: de ni lha dang mi la gsang //
T02TD1614E:139a-44: rgyud dang rgyud ni thams cad las //
T02TD1614E:139a-45: sba bar gsang ba yin par bshad //
T02TD1614E:139a-46: skye bo gnas la grong 'dab tu //
T02TD1614E:139a-47: gtor dang btung bas mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:139a-48: dbang po'i grong gis kun tu gang //
T02TD1614E:139a-49: 'dab ni lus la rnam par gnas //
T02TD1614E:139a-50: rang gi bdag po'i lha bsgoms la //
T02TD1614E:139a-51: nus pa yis ni mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:139a-52: lus kyi grong khyer spyi bor gnas //
T02TD1614E:139a-53: 'dab ni mtha' yi rnam par gnas //
T02TD1614E:139a-54: dbang du gnas pa'i nang gi gang /
T02TD1614E:139b-0: @139b grong gi 'dab ces bya bar bshad //
T02TD1614E:139b-1: grong khyer gang la gnas pa ni //
T02TD1614E:139b-2: skye ba'i byin gyi rlabs las byung //
T02TD1614E:139b-3: shes rab dbyings kyi dngos po ni //
T02TD1614E:139b-4: grong khyer bya ba'i ming du gsungs //
T02TD1614E:139b-5: rtse gcig pa dang rtse gnyis pa //
T02TD1614E:139b-6: gsum po dag ni bzhi mdo ru //
T02TD1614E:139b-7: lha yi mchod pa sngar bshams te //
T02TD1614E:139b-8: lam du gnas te mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:139b-9: las bcu la ni gnas pa ni //
T02TD1614E:139b-10: lam zhes pa ni lus la gnas //
T02TD1614E:139b-11: gcig pa rtog pa las byung ba //
T02TD1614E:139b-12: gnyis po gnyis kyis khyad par gyi //
T02TD1614E:139b-13: sum mdo theg pa'i khyad par du //
T02TD1614E:139b-14: rnal 'byor pas ni rtag ces bya //
T02TD1614E:139b-15: srog ni sum mdo zhes su gsungs //
T02TD1614E:139b-16: gsher dang dmar ser skam pa yi //
T02TD1614E:139b-17: bzhi mdo ru ni shes par bya //
T02TD1614E:139b-18: skyor ba la sogs rnam pa bzhi //
T02TD1614E:139b-19: steng dang 'og gi khyad par gyi //
T02TD1614E:139b-20: sum mdo zhes ni yongs su grags //
T02TD1614E:139b-21: steng du tshangs pa'i lam zhes bya //
T02TD1614E:139b-23: drag po dbus su rnam par shes //
T02TD1614E:139b-24: lam ni sum mdo dag tu bshad //
T02TD1614E:139b-25: gru bzhi yon tan kun ldan pa //
T02TD1614E:139b-26: gsang ba yi ni padmar gnas //
T02TD1614E:139b-27: gru gsum lam gsum du shes bya //
T02TD1614E:139b-28: gnyis kyis gzugs su gnyis su 'gro / gang tshe dngos po gcig gyur pa ;
T02TD1614E:139b-29: /'gro ba rnams kyis gnas kyi dngos //
T02TD1614E:139b-30: de ltar lam gcig shes bya ste //
T02TD1614E:139b-31: thar pa yi ni gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:139b-32: btab pa'i lam ni yongs thob pa'i //
T02TD1614E:139b-33: zhing brgyad du ni gnas par bya //
T02TD1614E:139b-34: shin tu dgod dang spyod pa'i gnas //
T02TD1614E:139b-35: de bzhin du ni rigs kyi ri //
T02TD1614E:139b-36: rgyal ba dang ni nye rgyal dang //
T02TD1614E:139b-37: de bzhin rab mchog chu yi gnas //
T02TD1614E:139b-38: char pa'i rtse dang de brgyad dang //
T02TD1614E:139b-39: de dag zhing zhes bya bar grags //
T02TD1614E:139b-40: gnas de dag tu 'dug gnas kyang //
T02TD1614E:139b-41: gtor ma aa yis mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:139b-42: zhing gi 'gram na gnas pa ni //
T02TD1614E:139b-43: nye ba yi ni zhing du bstan //
T02TD1614E:139b-44: zhing brgyad dag ni gnas rnams ni //
T02TD1614E:139b-45: lus la gnas pa'i bdag gis bshad //
T02TD1614E:139b-46: bla ma'i zhal snga'i bka' drin gyis //
T02TD1614E:139b-47: rim pa ci bzhin bdag gis dgrol //
T02TD1614E:139b-48: shin tu dgod pa kha la gnas //
T02TD1614E:139b-49: spyod ma'i gnas ni smin ma'i mtshams //
T02TD1614E:139b-50: rigs can rna ba dag tu brjod //
T02TD1614E:140a-0: rgyal ba sum mdo yi ni @140a * //
T02TD1614E:140a-2: nye rgyal de bzhin snying gar gsungs //
T02TD1614E:140a-3: rab mchog sna yi rtse mo la //
T02TD1614E:140a-4: chu yi gnas ni mig tu shes //
T02TD1614E:140a-5: char ba'i rtse mo spyi bor gnas //
T02TD1614E:140a-6: tshando ha ni sdom par gsungs //
T02TD1614E:140a-7: gsang ba yi ni padmar gnas //
T02TD1614E:140a-8: ze 'bru dang ni ze bar ldan //
T02TD1614E:140a-9: 'dab ma brgyad kyis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1614E:140a-10: de lta bas na brgyad du shes //
T02TD1614E:140a-11: ye shes dbang phyug ma dang ldan //
T02TD1614E:140a-12: lus ni zhing zhes bya bar gsungs //
T02TD1614E:140a-13: zhing ma shes rab tu shes bya //
T02TD1614E:140a-14: rnam pa kun gyis stong pas na //
T02TD1614E:140a-15: khyim stong du ni rab tu bshad //
T02TD1614E:140a-16: de na gnas pa'i lha rnams ni //
T02TD1614E:140a-17: cho ga snga mas mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:140a-18: dngos po thams cad rnam spangs pas //
T02TD1614E:140a-19: lus kyang stong pa nyid du brjod //
T02TD1614E:140a-20: khyim stong zhes pa lus la gzung //
T02TD1614E:140a-21: bsgom pas lha rnams bsgoms nas ni //
T02TD1614E:140a-22: sna tshogs mchod pa drug cho gas //
T02TD1614E:140a-23: rtag tu rnal 'byor pa yis mchod //
T02TD1614E:140a-24: gzugs kyi stong pa de nyid ltar //
T02TD1614E:140a-25: na di bcu po'ang de bzhin no //
T02TD1614E:140a-26: de la gnas pa'i ye shes ni //
T02TD1614E:140a-27: yid kyi sbyor bas mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:140a-28: stong pa'i ye shes rdo rje yis //
T02TD1614E:140a-29: gnas gang la ni rab gnas pa //
T02TD1614E:140a-30: chos 'byung zhes bya ba yi khyim //
T02TD1614E:140a-31: ye shes rnam shes dag dang ldan //
T02TD1614E:140a-32: de la gnas pa'i lha mo rnams //
T02TD1614E:140a-33: me tog chu yis mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:140a-34: sgrub pos dngos grub thob pa'i phyir //
T02TD1614E:140a-35: gsang ba las kyang gsang ba ste //
T02TD1614E:140a-36: gang dang gang du gang bsnyen pas //
T02TD1614E:140a-37: de phyir bsnyen pa zhes su gsungs //
T02TD1614E:140a-38: de dag las kyang gnas rgyu ru //
T02TD1614E:140a-39: gnas nas kyang ni mchog tu 'gro /'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las brgal ba'o //
T02TD1614E:140a-41: rab dga' la sogs sa brgyad dang //
T02TD1614E:140a-42: lags pa'i blo gros dang bcas dgu //
T02TD1614E:140a-43: zhing brgyad khyad par du brjod pa //
T02TD1614E:140a-44: zhing dgu'i bdag por shes par bya //
T02TD1614E:140a-45: 'dod pa srog ces byar bar shes //
T02TD1614E:140a-46: sa bon zhes bya dbang phyug go //
T02TD1614E:140a-47: 'dod pa las byung nga rgyal ni ;
T02TD1614E:140a-48: / de ni rdo rje 'dzin pa che //
T02TD1614E:140a-49: 'dod pa'i spyi bor yongs gnas te //
T02TD1614E:140a-50: rkang pa nas ni spyi bor khyab //
T02TD1614E:140a-51: 'dod pa gsum dor bab pas ni //
T02TD1614E:140a-52: der ni 'gro ba gsum po rmongs //
T02TD1614E:140a-53: sa la sogs pa de bzhin drug /'dod pa yi ni gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:140a-54: gzhan du bdud rtsi lnga yang brjod //
T02TD1614E:140b-0: @140b dbang phyug dang sogs dngos grub brgyad //
T02TD1614E:140b-1: mi rnams gang gis sgrub byed pa //
T02TD1614E:140b-2: chung ngu la sogs sgrub par ldan //
T02TD1614E:140b-3: 'dod pa lus kyi yan lag ste //
T02TD1614E:140b-4: de nas glang chen zhes su bshad //
T02TD1614E:140b-5: gnas de dag la gnas pa yi //
T02TD1614E:140b-6: lha rnams su ni rab grags pa //
T02TD1614E:140b-7: lnga po lnga po'i bdag nyid kyis //
T02TD1614E:140b-8: sngags pas rtag tu mchod par bya //
T02TD1614E:140b-9: dbang po phyogs nas brtsams nas ni //
T02TD1614E:140b-10: ji srid dbang ldan mtshams bar du //
T02TD1614E:140b-11: g-yas dang g-yon du bskor ba yi //
T02TD1614E:140b-12: rim pa brgyad pa shes par bya //
T02TD1614E:140b-13: dang po drag nag ces bya ba //
T02TD1614E:140b-14: rkang pa yi ni mthe bong bar //
T02TD1614E:140b-15: dus med drag po zhes grags pa //
T02TD1614E:140b-16: lha mo yi ni 'khor gyis bskor //
T02TD1614E:140b-17: gsang ba'i gnas su drag chen dang //
T02TD1614E:140b-18: lus kyi yan lag kun la khyab //
T02TD1614E:140b-19: lte ba'i gnas la lha byin te //
T02TD1614E:140b-20: sgyu ma yi ni gzugs kyi tshul //
T02TD1614E:140b-21: snying gar gnas pa'i nag po che //
T02TD1614E:140b-22: sgyu ma chen po mchog gi mchog / gtsigs pa kha yi phyogs gnas te //
T02TD1614E:140b-23: rdo rje mtshon ni mtshon chen po //
T02TD1614E:140b-24: 'jigs byed mchu la rtag tu gnas //
T02TD1614E:140b-26: mgo bor gnas pa dag pa che //
T02TD1614E:140b-27: tshangs pa'i bug las rnam par byung //
T02TD1614E:140b-28: sna yi bar du rtag gnas pa //
T02TD1614E:140b-29: bgegs kyi rgyal po gtso bo che //
T02TD1614E:140b-30: de dag mtshams su gnas pa ni //
T02TD1614E:140b-31: dbang ldan la sogs rim pa bzhin //
T02TD1614E:140b-32: tsa mu ndi ni mgo bo'i gnas //
T02TD1614E:140b-33: be t'a l'i ni shing la brten //
T02TD1614E:140b-34: a'a gho tsir ni sum mdor gnas //
T02TD1614E:140b-35: de nyid gsum po lam gsum bzhi //
T02TD1614E:140b-36: mgo zhes bya bar sgra chen po //
T02TD1614E:140b-37: bcu gnyis kyi ni mtshams su gnas //
T02TD1614E:140b-38: shin tu dgod pa dgod chen po //
T02TD1614E:140b-39: bgegs med kyi sa ni rnam par 'joms //
T02TD1614E:140b-40: bi bad tsha yis 'joms pa ste //
T02TD1614E:140b-41: snying ga yi ni padmar gnas //
T02TD1614E:140b-42: lha mo sgyu ma zhes su grags //
T02TD1614E:140b-43: 'gro rnams smos pas rmongs par bshad //
T02TD1614E:140b-44: lha mo au ma klad par gnas //
T02TD1614E:140b-45: klad pas ni tshugs 'dod pa ma //
T02TD1614E:140b-46: rgyal mo lha sogs lha mo che //
T02TD1614E:140b-47: na li yi ni gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:140b-48: pus mo byin pa nag po sogs //
T02TD1614E:140b-49: bzhi po dag ni chen po yin //
T02TD1614E:140b-50: dbang mo la sogs lha mo'i tshogs //
T02TD1614E:140b-51: snying ga yi ni padmar gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-0: gzugs la sogs pa'i bye brag drug / reg @141a * //
T02TD1614E:141a-1: bya yi ni gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-2: ze'u 'bru la ni aa yi gzugs //
T02TD1614E:141a-3: rdo rje sems dpa' rnam par bzhugs //
T02TD1614E:141a-4: ngag 'phrog la sogs lha mo che //
T02TD1614E:141a-5: nye ba'i na li bzhi por 'dod //
T02TD1614E:141a-6: ngag 'phrog ma ni gsang bar gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-7: 'bar byed ma ni spyir gnas te //
T02TD1614E:141a-8: sreg ma dang ni mched mar byed //
T02TD1614E:141a-9: dbang phyug chen mo me yi gzugs //
T02TD1614E:141a-10: 'jib byed ma ni rkan la gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-11: rlung gi gzugs can dbang phyug ngag /'jigs pa'i gzugs kyi lha mo ni //
T02TD1614E:141a-13: lce yi rtsa bar gnas pa yi //
T02TD1614E:141a-14: de ni chu yi gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-15: 'jigs byed la sogs lha mo bzhi //
T02TD1614E:141a-16: lam bzhi ru ni gnas pa yin //
T02TD1614E:141a-18: de ni sgra yi gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-19: thod pa'i phreng gis phreng bcings pa'i //
T02TD1614E:141a-20: lha mo bzhi ni chen mo yin //
T02TD1614E:141a-21: thig le gnas na rtags 'byung ba //
T02TD1614E:141a-22: shakti yi ni gzugs su gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-23: ral gri la sogs 'dzin pas brgyan //
T02TD1614E:141a-24: lag pa dang ni rkang par gzhag /'dod pa la sogs nyon mongs gcod //
T02TD1614E:141a-25: rgol ba thams cad phyi mthar byed //
T02TD1614E:141a-26: bgegs rnams thams cad 'joms pa'i lta //
T02TD1614E:141a-28: zhi sogs las kyi dngos grub dang ;
T02TD1614E:141a-29: / mkha' 'gro ma la sgrub pa la //
T02TD1614E:141a-30: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku chen po //
T02TD1614E:141a-31: rdo rje sems dpa' khyab pa'i gtso //
T02TD1614E:141a-32: bdag nyid de ltar bsgoms nas ni //
T02TD1614E:141a-33: kun tu sngags pa yis ni mchod //
T02TD1614E:141a-34: bza' dang btung ba gos dag kyang //
T02TD1614E:141a-35: phreng ba dri dang gos la sogs //
T02TD1614E:141a-36: lus kyi de nyid la gnas te //
T02TD1614E:141a-37: rnal 'byor rig pas rtag tu mchod //
T02TD1614E:141a-38: ji ltar de nyid rjes 'brang ste //
T02TD1614E:141a-39: de yi gtor las cho ga bshad //
T02TD1614E:141a-40: khrag ni rab tu mchod sbyin te //
T02TD1614E:141a-41: chu yi gnas ni de bzhin nya //
T02TD1614E:141a-42: til gyi khur ba char ba'i rtse //
T02TD1614E:141a-43: shin tu dgod pa mkhur skya ba //
T02TD1614E:141a-44: kha dog lnga pa spyod pa'i gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-45: sha ni rigs kyi ri'u gsungs //
T02TD1614E:141a-46: a'a li de bzhin rgyal ba'i gnas //
T02TD1614E:141a-47: nye bar rgyal ba'i ba dan gsungs //
T02TD1614E:141a-48: zhi brgyad kyis ni mtshan pa'o //
T02TD1614E:141a-49: de nas zhing gi bdag po rnams bshad par bya ste //
T02TD1614E:141a-50: shar phyogs su ni shin tu dgod pa la //
T02TD1614E:141b-0: zhi ba'i mig can gser bsreg pa'i mdog lta @141b bu phyag na rdo rje bsnams shing ka dam ba la gnas pa'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-1: me'i phyogs su ni spyod pa nag mo'i lha mo kha dog dmar mo //
T02TD1614E:141b-2: phyag na shakti bsnams shing ka ranydza la gnas pa'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-3: lho phyogs su ni ki li gi ris mtshan pa'i lha chen po kha dog nag po dbyug pa bsnams pa'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-4: bden bral du ni rgyal ba can te /
T02TD1614E:141b-5: shing nim pa la gnas pa /
T02TD1614E:141b-6: phyag na ral gri bsnams pa du ba'i mdog can zhal 'bar ba dang /
T02TD1614E:141b-7: nub phyogs su ni nye rgyal te sgyu 'phrul chen po dang /
T02TD1614E:141b-8: shing aa shvattha la gnas pa'i zhags pa bsnams pa'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-9: rlung gi phyogs su ni mchod sbyin la rlung gi shugs can te /
T02TD1614E:141b-10: ba dan bsnams shing rlung gi mdog can shing au dum b'a ra la gnas pa'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-11: byang gi phyogs su ni shing ka ri dbyug pa bsnams pa la /
T02TD1614E:141b-12: kha dog ser bo shing ta la la gnas pa'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-13: dbang ldan gyi phyogs su ni char pa'i rtse la rna bo che /
T02TD1614E:141b-14: mdog dmar po rtse gsum pa bsnams pa /
T02TD1614E:141b-15: shing wa ta la gnas pa'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-16: de dag ni shing gi bdag por shes par bya zhing mkha' 'gro ma lnga'i rang bzhin nyid do //
T02TD1614E:141b-17: karkada dang ro hi ta ni sna'i steng du'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-18: chu srin dang mo hi ta ni sna'i 'og tu'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-19: bi b'a dang tsa ba na dang /
T02TD1614E:141b-20: kshum dang du ba dang me'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-21: seng ge dang mi ki ri dang /
T02TD1614E:141b-29: de dag sna bug g-yas pa la'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-30: glang dang kum ma dang kshmryum dang ro tsa na dang me'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-31: bum pa dang mo hi ta dang /
T02TD1614E:141b-32: hmryum dang dri med gsum dang sa'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-33: nya dang bha tra dang smryum dang chu dang sa'i gdugs so //
T02TD1614E:141b-34: 'khrig pa dang chu srin dang ymryum dang dbye ba dang rlung ngo //
T02TD1614E:141b-35: de dag sna bug g-yon pa la'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-36: srid dang aam dang ye shes dang /
T02TD1614E:141b-37: rdo rje sems dpa' dang nam mkha'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-38: aa dang ye shes mkha' 'gro ma dang //
T02TD1614E:141b-39: lug dang rnam par shes pa dang /
T02TD1614E:141b-41: bla ma'i zhal gyi rim pa 'di ni dngos grub 'dod pa'i phyir gsang bar bya'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-42: dang po la ni nor btang bya //
T02TD1614E:141b-43: gnyis pa la ni nor bsdu'o //
T02TD1614E:141b-44: gsum pa la ni zhing las bya //
T02TD1614E:141b-45: bzhi pa la ni sa bon gdab //
T02TD1614E:141b-46: lnga pa la ni khyim du 'jug//
T02TD1614E:142a-0: @142a * // drug pa la ni khyim bzhi'i gnas //
T02TD1614E:142a-1: bdun pa la ni las bya ba //
T02TD1614E:142a-2: gos dang rgyan dang longs spyod rdzogs //
T02TD1614E:142a-3: song ba dag ni phyir mi ldog / sangs rgyas dngos grub sgrub rnams kyis //
T02TD1614E:142a-4: bla ma mchod phyir rang phyag rgya //
T02TD1614E:142a-5: rang gi phyag rgya bstan pa yis //
T02TD1614E:142a-6: dngos grub thob par rgyud las gsungs //
T02TD1614E:142a-7: gzhan las dngos grub thob mi 'gyur //
T02TD1614E:142a-8: phyi rol bskul pas dam tshig med //
T02TD1614E:142a-9: dpal ldan sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
T02TD1614E:142a-10: slob dpon byang chub rdo rje nyid //
T02TD1614E:142a-11: dngos rnams sgyu ma lta bu la //
T02TD1614E:142a-12: spro ba dang ni bsdu ba mdzad //
T02TD1614E:142a-13: rnal 'byor chen po skal ldan rnams//
T02TD1614E:142a-14: sdig pa rnams ni rnam byang zhing //
T02TD1614E:142a-15: bsod nams rnams ni 'phel ba rnams //
T02TD1614E:142a-16: bde ba can du 'gro par shog / shing gcig pa'i dka' 'grel slob dpon 'phags pa'i lha'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so//
